OPTIVISION TECHN said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 41.06% to NT$51,610,000 from NT$87,570,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales             51,610           87,570    
YOY%             -41.06%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            412,904          549,514    
YOY%             -24.86% 
=================================================================
 